                    <i class="text-danger">.</i><p>To quickly process your transactions.</p>
                    <i class="text-danger">.</i><p>To send periodic emails regarding your order or other products and services.</p>

                    	<h3 class=" text-danger"><i>How do we protect visitor information?</i></h3>
                    <p>Our website is scanned on a regular basis for security holes and known vulnerabilities in order to make your visit to our site as safe as possible.
                        <br />
We use regular Malware Scanning.
